<section class="about-story section-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="story-content">
      <div class="story-text">
        <h2 class="heading-lg">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="body-text">Founded in {{ site.business.established }}, Jiffyprints began with a simple mission: to provide businesses and individuals with high-quality custom embroidery and printing services that they could count on. What started as a small Toronto-based operation has grown into a trusted partner for customers across Canada.</p>
        
        <p class="body-text">Our focus has always been on embroidery excellence. We believe that embroidered designs offer unmatched durability and professional appearance, making them perfect for corporate uniforms, team apparel, and promotional items that need to withstand frequent use and washing.</p>
        
        <p class="body-text">Over the years, we've expanded our services to include DTF printing, DTG printing, and screen printing, but embroidery remains at the heart of what we do. Our commitment to quality, fast turnaround times, and personalized service has made us the go-to choice for businesses across Canada.</p>
      </div>
      
